'''Novacom''' was [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan's]] largest [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] provider at the time of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destruction]]. The company was owned by the father of [[Tycho Celchu/Legends|Tycho Celchu]]. The company owned a [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] cabin near [[Wuitho Trifalls]] on Alderaan.

